Introduction

Lara Rajagopalan is a American/Tamilian-Indian singer and dancer under Geffen Records and HYBE Labels. She is best known as a member of the global girl group KATSEYE.

Lara is recognized for her participation in the survival show "The Debut: Dream Academy", where she ranked 2nd and qualified for debut, becoming a member of the girl group KATSEYE.

On August 16, 2024, Lara officially debuted as a member of KATSEYE with their first EP "SIS (SOFT IS STRONG)".
